wdi2-NY.GDP.DEFL.ZS.def: The GDP implicit deflator is the ratio of GDP in current local currency to GDP in constant local currency. The base year varies by country.
wdi2-NY.GDP.DEFL.ZS.name: GDP deflator
wdi2-NY.GDP.DEFL.ZS.source: World Bank national accounts data, and OECD National Accounts data files.
